{"tid":690161,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"但有一個夢，不會死，記著吧；無論雨怎麼打，雲加仍是會好波 ！","createTime":"2018-06-04T15:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T02:22:00.000Z","uid":36497,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2433f94b1c2dd1825d495b3039ee2f392a13a46e","tid":690161,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2014/06/1304151528482436-594x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F06%2F1304151528482436-594x400.jpg&h=98f233c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/233845_2b9660a20da8aa47fad665a5d10c2aab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F233845_2b9660a20da8aa47fad665a5d10c2aab.jpg&h=4ae8de20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n忘不了的　零四也不會蠶蝕<br />\n雲加深處始終也記憶那年那夕<br />\n曾經痛惜　年月裏轉化為力<br />\n一點真理　一個理想永遠地尋覓<br />\n<br />\n悠悠長長雲加前航不懂去驚怕<br />\n荊荊棘棘反雲斬去不必多看它<br />\n浮浮沉沉昨日迷雲雖不說一話<br />\n不想清楚分析太多真心抑意假<br />\n<br />\n但有一個夢　不會死　記著吧<br />\n無論雨怎麼打　雲加仍是會好波<br />\n但有一個夢　阿仙奴　記著吧<br />\n來自阿迷的心　記著吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n忘不了的　留下了不敗意識<br />\n雲加相信始終會變真某年某夕<br />\n如此訊息　仍賴你跟我全力<br />\n雲加好波　將這理想繼續在尋覓<br />\n<br />\n悠悠長長雲加前航不懂去驚怕<br />\n荊荊棘棘反雲斬去不必多看它<br />\n浮浮沉沉昨日迷雲雖不說一話<br />\n不想清楚分析太多真心抑意假<br />\n<br />\n但有一個夢　不會死　記著吧<br />\n無論雨怎麼打　雲加仍是會好波<br />\n但有一個夢　阿仙奴　記著吧<br />\n來自阿迷的心　記著吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9562f9f1ae8fedf7b259571aefd73f096182eea5","tid":690161,"uid":71398,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"毋忘雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3148f489e8f4202e678c71093496aa43db92562","tid":690161,"uid":38841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9562f9f1ae